{"tid":1710094,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【究極鎖魔法】用一人之力癱瘓一條港鐵線","createTime":"2019-11-12T05:32:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T06:02:14.000Z","uid":64981,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fbf222df74d4cd41d81ff0f079a2cae0846354c5","tid":1710094,"uid":64981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:32:07.000Z","msg":"大家睇咗呢篇文先<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/10/21/lock-on/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2019%2F10%2F21%2Flock-on%2F&d=UyoO8KdNfTPb55o7yEEco13VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=1434dda9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/10/21/lock-on/</a><br />\n<blockquote><strong>「鎖魔法」：和理非的最大武器 2019年10月21日 BY BILLY TONG</strong><br />\n<br />\n在外國的和理非示威，有「緊鎖戰術」（lock-on）的傳統，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">示威者以單車鏈、手扣、或者各種大鐵鎖和鋼管，把自己緊鎖在一個地方，進行公民抗命。</span></strong>其中最早的例子，是女權主義者 Muriel Matters，她致力爭取女性投票權。從前，英國女士不單沒有投票權，旁聽會議，也要在英國下議院女賓廊（The Ladies&rsquo; Gallery）隔著鐵欄觀看。在 1908 年，Muriel Matters 和友人 Helen Fox 把自己鎖於女賓廊的鐵欄上，高叫口號，發表演說，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">國會職員無法把她們的鎖鏈解開，只能把整個鐵欄拆掉，然後帶走她們</span></strong>，整場運動別具象徵意義，十年後，部分英國女性被賦予投票權。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n某啲港鐵嘅路線每逢到尾站，都要清曬所有乘客，先會將列車送走，再派新車出黎。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>試想像下，如果我地將用單車鎖自己鎖喺扶手度，然後到尾站都賴死唔走，會發生咩事？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>好處：</strong><br />\n車上面嘅乘客唔會畀壓力你（班自私撚已經上曬岸離開咗車廂理撚得你）、<br />\n一人之力阻礙兩班列車甚至成條路線嘅運作（全部車都埋唔到尾站都唔知點算）、<br />\n降低風險（覺得唔對路／港鐵狗畀好大壓力你咪開鎖即刻走）、<br />\n引起反響（如果有傳媒報個話又係香港抗爭蜚聲國際嘅機會）<br />\n<br />\n開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7fb2151764804486c5001bbfd05921b5c954ac8","tid":1710094,"uid":64981,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/GettyIm8793.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2FGettyIm8793.jpg&h=84ff4d43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f388c388a7d1cf61636853e3596479c0edb486f2","tid":1710094,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:33:08.000Z","msg":"［全民罷工妙計］繁忙時間要引狗衝入港鐵站向返工人士施襲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1708303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1708303</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f9a573f4b4479b99987a694ec1529e08407beb48","tid":1710094,"uid":64981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:33:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Get10924-1200x798.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2FGet10924-1200x798.jpg&h=d7d72a53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cdd4f7eb6d730c3cd30b41ab9f019f4891291117","tid":1710094,"uid":64981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:34:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://c1.thejournal.ie/media/2019/07/008-extinction-rebellion-protest_90575071-390x285.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.thejournal.ie%2Fmedia%2F2019%2F07%2F008-extinction-rebellion-protest_90575071-390x285.jpg&h=56dc90ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8b12a05186e8c1a68f8900264d1cef200ee8041","tid":1710094,"uid":1142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:34:34.000Z","msg":"如果比人打 比狗係咁噴椒?"},{"pid":"fec3ab549d41b0b048ff07dc7670c66a7e284d0e","tid":1710094,"uid":238920,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:34:49.000Z","msg":"你鎖鳩自己係扶手度<br />\n咪成班廢老打鳩你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br